title: the who my generation title font
content:
sorry for the poor quality image. Can anyone tell me the title font for this album cover. thanks.

comments.content:
This is obviously pre-digital. It reminds me of Akzidenz Grotesk condensed bold or Helvetica Inserat.  
Can't tell well from the scan - the letterforms look a little more square than both of these.
